OL,3,C'Burn until your skin is no more': Man
OL,4,Cwho threatened MP Jess Phillips jailed
OL,6,FA man who emailed Labour MP Jess
OL,7,FPhillips saying she would "burn until
OL,8,Fher skin is no more" has been jailed.
OL,10,FNabil Arif, 36, from Birmingham, was
OL,11,Falso given a restraining order barring
OL,12,Fhim from contacting the MP until
OL,13,Ffurther notice.
OL,15,FArif had sent threatening emails over
OL,16,Fthe space of four months from October
OL,17,Flast year before she reported him to
OL,18,Fthe police.
