OL,3,C'Burn until your skin is no more': Man
OL,4,Cwho threatened MP Jess Phillips jailed
OL,6,FIn the final email Arif said she was
OL,7,F'pathetic' and that she would 'burn
OL,8,Funtil her skin is no more'.
OL,10,FIn other emails Arfi told Ms Philips
OL,11,F"hell is real, and you will burn".
OL,13,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,14,Fsaid the emails were related to the
OL,15,FIsrael/Gaza conflict.
