OL,3,C'Burn until your skin is no more': Man
OL,4,Cwho threatened MP Jess Phillips jailed
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read out
OL,7,Fto the court, Ms Phillips expressed
OL,8,Ffear that Arif's aggression towards
OL,9,Fher might escalate and potentially
OL,10,Flead to her coming to physical harm at
OL,11,Fhis hands, which she said had changed
OL,12,Fher life "immeasurably".
OL,14,F"It had limited my freedom and my
OL,15,Fability to do my job closely with the
OL,16,Fpublic as I used to do," she said.
