OL,3,C'Burn until your skin is no more': Man
OL,4,Cwho threatened MP Jess Phillips jailed
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fsaid Arif, of Warwick Road,
OL,8,FBirmingham, was sentenced on Monday at
OL,9,FBirmingham Magistrates' Court to 12
OL,10,Fweeks in custody and was also made
OL,11,Fsubject of a restraining order barring
OL,12,Fhim from contacting the MP until
OL,13,Ffurther notice.
OL,15,FHe was convicted of sending, by public
OL,16,Fcommunication network, an offensive,
OL,17,Findecent, obscene or menacing message
OL,18,For matter following a trial at the
OL,19,Fsame court on July 29.
