OL,3,C'Burn until your skin is no more': Man
OL,4,Cwho threatened MP Jess Phillips jailed
OL,6,FRichard Purchase of the CPS said:
OL,7,F"Members of Parliament have a right to
OL,8,Fperform their duties and represent
OL,9,Ftheir constituents without being
OL,10,Fsubjected to derogatory messages that
OL,11,Fcause alarm and distress.
OL,13,F"It is clear that Nabil Arif's
OL,14,Fbehaviour escalated from the initial
OL,15,Femails, leading Ms Phillips to fear
OL,16,Ffor her safety."
